ious folks by subscribing here:
Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,=20
Happy Tuesday and welcome back to our fourth Not Boring Deep Dive on Ramp [=
 https://substack.com/redirect/f1cac6f5-8e25-4004-b26e-a9641b7b566b?j=3DeyJ=
1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ].=20
Ramp is one of the fastest-growing, best-run startups in the world. It=E2=
=80=99s also just one of my favorites. I met Ramp CEO Eric Glyman the first=
