rline;">Ramp</a><span>. </span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font=
-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Ramp is one of the fas=
test-growing, best-run startups in the world. It&#8217;s also just one of m=
y favorites. I met Ramp CEO Eric Glyman the first year I wrote Not Boring, =
invested personally in the company before I had a fund, and have invested v=
ia Not Boring Capital twice. </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-s=
ize: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">I haven&#8217;t written =
about any other company more than once, but Ramp has become a tradition her=
e, and I learn something totally new every time. </p><p style=3D"color: rgb=
(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">This=
 time, it&#8217;s AI. Specifically, what will the B2B software landscape lo=
ok like as companies build AI into their products? What will the experience=
 of using software at work be like? </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55);=
 font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Software is not d=
ead, but I do think B2B will consolidate. There will be some massive winner=
s, the ones who can help take all of the work that people in a particular d=
epartment hate off their plates. And if you&#8217;re going to choose a depa=
rtment, finance is a good one to choose: finance controls the purse strings=
, and it touches every piece of the organization, even ones that don&#8217;=
t seem like &#8220;finance.&#8221;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); f=
ont-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Like Travel. =
Today, Ramp is launching </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/2c=
0d9055-90d1-4922-acbc-a3d0261c2707?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaM=
ZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decor=
ation: underline;">Ramp Travel</a><span>, which means you can now book trav=
el right through Ramp. I tried it, and it&#8217;s predictably great. </span=
></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px=
; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">It also points to a world in which you just hand ove=
r your card to an AI agent and let it do all of the booking for you &#8212;=
 to save you time and money, and let you focus on the parts of your job tha=
t you actually like doing.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size=
: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Let&#8217;s get to it. </p>=
