rline;">Better Tools, Bigger Companies</a></em><span>, I wrote: &#8220;SaaS=
 isn&#8217;t dead. There will be big SaaS businesses built, and in particul=
ar, </span><strong>today&#8217;s leading SaaS companies will get much bigge=
r as they marry their place in customers&#8217; workflows with AI to delive=
r more value</strong><span>. Information industries will be won with softwa=
re.&#8221;&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 1=
